(b)        “Board” means the Pakistan Ordnance Factories Board constituted under this
Ordinance;
(c)        “Chairman” means the Chairman of the Board;
(d)        “factory” means an ordnance factory owned by the 2[Federal Government];
(e)        “member” means a member of the Board.
